name: Ja Ri_002, image
description: A fragment from a collaboration between visual artist rollinos (@rollinos) and Brazilian artist Jadsa (@jadsaaa). The frame is part of the visual work for 'Ja Ri',track from  "Olho de Vidro", Jadsa's breakthrough first record released by Balaclava Records. The work was commissioned by Music Video Festival(www.musicvideofestival.com.br).Series of 3 different frames.
